{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/books","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I like learn, explain and, when time gives me a chance, write. Write and transmit knowledge is complicated and requires time, at least for me, to structure what to say and how to say it.</p>\n<p>As Albert Einstein said: <em><strong>If you can't explain it simply, you don't understand it well enough</strong></em>.</p>\n<h2>The NodeJS cluster module</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://leanpub.com/thenodejsclustermodule\">The NodeJS cluster module</a> is a short book, extracted from this post articles, introducing the NodeJS cluster module. NodeJS processes runs on a single process, which means it does not take advantage from multi-core systems by default. If you have an 8 core CPU and run a NodeJS program via $ node app.js it will run in a single process, wasting the rest of CPUs.</p>\n<p>Hopefully for us NodeJS offers the cluster module that contains a set of functions and properties that help us to create programs that uses all the CPUs.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 300px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 139.8773006134969%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"thenodecluestermodule\"\n        title=\"thenodecluestermodule\"\n        src=\"/static/1de9f186b6470b6165f941e34d1108c9/5a46d/thenodecluestermodule.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1de9f186b6470b6165f941e34d1108c9/222b7/thenodecluestermodule.png 163w,\n/static/1de9f186b6470b6165f941e34d1108c9/5a46d/thenodecluestermodule.png 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>LeanPub link: <a href=\"https://leanpub.com/thenodejsclustermodule\">https://leanpub.com/thenodejsclustermodule</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>The Book of OpenLayers3</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/books/the-book-of-openlayers3\">The Book of OpenLayers3</a>: Published on 2014, just before the first release of OpenLayers3 was release, the book covers the most important topics of this awesome web mapping library.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/books/the-book-of-openlayers3\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 301px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 130.06134969325154%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"thebookofopenlayers3\"\n        title=\"thebookofopenlayers3\"\n        src=\"/static/85e2cdaabdd47ef77b762d7f9092eee8/e8ddc/thebookofopenlayers3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/85e2cdaabdd47ef77b762d7f9092eee8/d2f63/thebookofopenlayers3.jpg 163w,\n/static/85e2cdaabdd47ef77b762d7f9092eee8/e8ddc/thebookofopenlayers3.jpg 301w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 301px) 100vw, 301px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>LeanPub link: <a href=\"https://leanpub.com/thebookofopenlayers3\">https://leanpub.com/thebookofopenlayers3</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>OpenLayers Cookbook</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/books/openlayers-cookbook\">OpenLayers Cookbook</a>: Published on 2012, this cookbook covers the most common situations of the day to day work with OpenLayers 2.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"/books/openlayers-cookbook\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 302px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 123.31288343558282%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"openlayers-cookbook\"\n        title=\"openlayers-cookbook\"\n        src=\"/static/99c01733248e8e53a81f05020d6d48cc/7a297/7843OS_OpenLayer%20Cookbook_cov_0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/99c01733248e8e53a81f05020d6d48cc/d2f63/7843OS_OpenLayer%20Cookbook_cov_0.jpg 163w,\n/static/99c01733248e8e53a81f05020d6d48cc/7a297/7843OS_OpenLayer%20Cookbook_cov_0.jpg 302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 302px) 100vw, 302px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>","excerpt":"I like learn, explain and, when time gives me a chance, write. Write and transmit knowledge is complicated and requires time, at least for me, to structure what…","frontmatter":{"date":"23 December, 2014","title":"Books"},"fields":{"slug":null,"readingTime":{"text":"2 min read"}}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["2080290373","63159454"]}